---
title: Roast Turkey Thanksgiving Feast A traditional dinner with all the sides you love! | 8-10 servings
description: ***Please note that the turkey and sides will ship in a separate boxes.***

This complete holiday feast is one more thing to add to your list of things to be thankful for! We took care of the planning (and shopping!), so you can spend more time enjoying the company of friends and family this Thanksgiving. We’ll help you get this impressive holiday meal on the table with the least amount of stress possible. On the menu: Roast Turkey with Garlic Herb Butter Rub and Classic Gravy for the main event, plus Creamy Mashed Potatoes, fluffy Brioche Stuffing, roasted Garlic Green Beans, and Fresh Cranberry Sauce on the side. Don’t worry, we included dessert too! You’ll finish the meal with warm Apple Crisp with Cinnamon Pecan Crumble.

*Download recipe card for complete nutrition information.*
